  "title": "Create: Buffer & Beams",
  "description": "Have you ever wanted train features to your create trains? Well that’s what Create: Buffer & Beams is!",
  "body": "<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Buffer &amp; Beams</strong></h2>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>The mod to spice up your Create Mod trains.</em></h4>\n<hr />\n<p>Trailer:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><em><strong><u>COMING SOON&hellip;</u></strong></em></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This is in 1.5 but, there is a known issue about Z-Fighting read about it <a href=\"https://github.com/createbufferandbeams/createbufferandbeams-stable/issues/1\">here.</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Create: Buffer &amp; Beams is a train related extension for Create and for the people who like or enjoy trains and locomotives.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Older Versions avalible&nbsp;on Curseforge ( 1.0 and prior )</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">.<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/create-buffers-beams/\"><img class=\"image_resized\" style=\"width: 227px;\" src=\"https://33333.cdn.cke-cs.com/kSW7V9NHUXugvhoQeFaf/images/4b3a6647c243f931f3b94456960be66c721e1da79dc09a11.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://33333.cdn.cke-cs.com/kSW7V9NHUXugvhoQeFaf/images/4b3a6647c243f931f3b94456960be66c721e1da79dc09a11.png/w_96 96w, https://33333.cdn.cke-cs.com/kSW7V9NHUXugvhoQeFaf/images/4b3a6647c243f931f3b94456960be66c721e1da79dc09a11.png/w_176 176w, https://33333.cdn.cke-cs.com/kSW7V9NHUXugvhoQeFaf/images/4b3a6647c243f931f3b94456960be66c721e1da79dc09a11.png/w_256 256w\" width=\"256\" height=\"227\" /><img src=\"https://33333.cdn.cke-cs.com/kSW7V9NHUXugvhoQeFaf/images/5c753ef605569087a71a38ae082e3968e54ef9f0b4d8d0c2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"308\" height=\"233\" /></a><a href=\"https://github.com/createbufferandbeams/createbufferandbeams-stable\"><img src=\"https://33333.cdn.cke-cs.com/kSW7V9NHUXugvhoQeFaf/images/ddbaafdc9422f6285e00c44c8cfb8d9796978b0e88c7fd98.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"230\" height=\"230\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
